  "description": "<p>7月17日出版的美国《纽约时报》印刷版刊文称，虽然iPhone等潮流电子产品在世界各地广受追捧，但在光鲜之下，却隐匿着一群生活在边缘地带的年轻人。<strong>他们跟果粉一样有着自己的梦想，但迫于生计，却不得不在乏味的生产线上充当“螺丝钉”。对他们来说，利用宝贵的业余时间享受青春是难得的奢侈，但也恰 恰是他们重返生产线的动力所在。郑州富士康工厂便提供了这样一个样本，让我们得以一窥这些年轻人的别样青春。</strong></p><img border=\"0\" height=\"1\" src=\"http://cnbeta.feedsportal.com/c/34306/f/624776/s/2ec5bf82/mf.gif\" width=\"1\" /><div class=\"mf-viral\"><table border=\"0\"><tr><td valign=\"middle\"><a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/twitter/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245043.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E7%8B%82%E6%AC%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/twitter.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/facebook/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245043.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E7%8B%82%E6%AC%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/facebook.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/linkedin/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245043.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E7%8B%82%E6%AC%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/linkedin.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/share/gplus/?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbeta.com%2Farticles%2F245043.htm&amp;t=%E5%AF%8C%E5%A3%AB%E5%BA%B7%E9%87%8C%E7%9A%84%E5%B9%B4%E8%BD%BB%E4%BA%BA%EF%BC%9A%E8%BE%B9%E7%BC%98%E5%9C%B0%E5%B8%A6%E7%9A%84%E9%9D%92%E6%98%A5%E7%8B%82%E6%AC%A2\" target=\"_blank\"><img border=\"0\" src=\"http://res3.feedsportal.com/social/googleplus.png\" /></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"http://share.feedsportal.com/sha